<br />
<br />My next option is my Nes Toploader with the Bars that looks horrible.  I read all 7 pages of the "top loader - getting rid of bad video, lets figure this out!" and got so confused there are like so many guides  but which one to follow. I am poor at reading a diagram but can solder wire easy just need  pictures for each step. Or someone to write me a detailed instruction for each step due to my lack of reading a diagram.  If anyone wants to take the time to PM the info and help me through it I will take all the pictures and Post the Idiot proof Guide to this and put this thing to bed wants and for all.
<br />
<br />Or, my last  option is go with a clone.  The only games I have that would be obscure that might not work would be Death Race, Maniac Mansion, Zelda Outlands Repo, EarthBound Repo.  DO game Genuie work on the clones which one is the Best?
<br />
